Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:10.11,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.14,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an2\fad(250,250)}I'm so
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.14,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8\fad(250,250)}I'm so
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:14.08,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}聞けない弱虫で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:14.08,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}是一個不聽話的膽小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:14.74,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an2\fad(250,250)}I know
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:14.74,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8\fad(250,250)}I know
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.45,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}とはいえ好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.45,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}話雖如此 但喜歡二字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:20.42,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}真顔じゃ困る
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:20.42,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}一臉認真地說會很苦惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:23.82,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}居心地いいキミの隣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:23.82,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}待在你身邊就覺得很舒心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:27.29,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}不器用すぎだねふたり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:27.29,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}兩個人都太笨拙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:33.57,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}ぎこちなく歩幅あわせて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:33.57,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}笨拙地配合腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:37.90,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}ジタバタするキミの隣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:37.90,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}待在慌慌張張的你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.60,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}転がるように恋しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.60,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}談一場快要摔到似的戀愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:47.43,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}1ミリずつ解ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:47.43,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}一毫米一毫米地了解彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:51.10,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}きっと
